cburnett — chess piece SVG set (web app)
https://github.com/lichess-org/lila

The chess piece SVGs in web/public/pieces/ (wK.svg 等 12 files) are the
"cburnett" set bundled with Lichess (lila), located at
public/piece/cburnett/ in the lichess-org/lila repository. The cburnett set
was created by Colin M.L. Burnett and is distributed under the GNU General
Public License, version 2 or later (GPLv2+):
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-2.0.html
Original artwork: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User:Cburnett/GFDL_images/Chess

The app logo / PWA icons (web/public/title-logo.svg, web/public/favicon.svg,
web/assets/icon*.svg and the PNGs generated from them) contain a knight
silhouette derived from the cburnett knight (wN.svg) and are likewise
distributed under GPLv2+.
