Stockfish / Stockfish.js — chess engine (web app)
https://github.com/official-stockfish/Stockfish
https://github.com/nmrugg/stockfish.js

The web app (web/) bundles the Stockfish chess engine compiled to WebAssembly
via Stockfish.js by Nathan Rugg (nmrugg). The single-thread "lite" build files
(web/public/engine/stockfish-*-lite-single.js and .wasm) are vendored from the
npm package "stockfish" into public/engine/ at install/build time by
web/scripts/copy-engine.mjs.

